{"translation-revision-date":"2026-04-09 06:41:27+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=n != 1;","lang":"es"},"Pro - lifetime":["Pro - de por vida"],"Pro-lifetime":["Pro-de por vida"],"You must first activate your plugin license before redeeming a credit code.":["Primero debes activar la licencia de tu plugin antes de canjear un c\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito."],"Done":["Hecho"],"Redeem":["Canjear"],"Redeeming...":["Canjeando..."],"Enter your credit code":["Introduce tu c\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito"],"Credit code":["C\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito"],"An error occurred.":["Ocurri\u00f3 un error."],"Please enter a credit code.":["Por favor, introduce un c\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito."],"OK":["Vale"],"Where to find my credit codes?":["\u00bfD\u00f3nde puedo encontrar mis c\u00f3digos de cr\u00e9dito?"],"No credits found for your Pro license. Please buy or redeem credits to use the remote scan feature.":["No se han encontrado acreditaciones para tu licencia Pro. Compra o canjea cr\u00e9ditos para usar la caracter\u00edstica de exploraci\u00f3n por remoto."],"You have reached your daily limit for remote server requests. Please wait for your credits to reset.":["Has alcanzado tu l\u00edmite diario de solicitudes al servidor remoto. Por favor, espera a que se restablezcan tus cr\u00e9ditos."],"Buy credits":["Comprar cr\u00e9ditos"],"Last info refresh:":["\u00daltima actualizaci\u00f3n de informaci\u00f3n:"],"Daily limit will reset in:":["El l\u00edmite diario se restablecer\u00e1 en:"],"(You have used all your credits)":["(Has utilizado todos tus cr\u00e9ditos)"],"(You have %s credits left)":["(Te quedan %s cr\u00e9ditos)"],"Total credits used:":["Cr\u00e9ditos totales utilizados:"],"This credit code has already been redeemed. Please close this pop-up and click the 'Refresh credits info' button to refresh your credit balance":["Este c\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito ya ha sido canjeado. Por favor, cierra esta ventana emergente y haz clic en el bot\u00f3n \u00abActualizar informaci\u00f3n de cr\u00e9ditos\u00bb para actualizar tu balance de cr\u00e9dito."],"Refresh credits info":["Actualizar informaci\u00f3n de cr\u00e9ditos"],"Redeem credit code":["Canjear c\u00f3digo de cr\u00e9dito"],"Remote Scan Credits:":["Cr\u00e9ditos de exploraci\u00f3n por remoto:"],"License expiration date format (e.g. December 10, 2025)\u0004F j, Y":["F j, Y"],"Saving...":["Guardando\u2026"],"Calculating...":["Calculando..."],"Cleanup method":["M\u00e9todo de limpieza"],"Direct SQL queries":["Consultas SQL directas"],"Native WP functions":["Funciones nativas de WP"],"This method uses direct SQL queries for cleanup operations. This can be faster but may bypass some WordPress mechanisms. For example, when deleting trashed posts, this method will directly remove the posts from the database without triggering associated hooks and actions, which may leave related metadata, taxonomies, and other linked data intact and potentially lead to extra orphaned items.":["Este m\u00e9todo utiliza consultas SQL directas para las operaciones de limpieza. Puede ser m\u00e1s r\u00e1pido, pero puede obviar algunos mecanismos de WordPress. Por ejemplo, al borrar entradas eliminadas, este m\u00e9todo las eliminar\u00e1 directamente de la base de datos sin activar los ganchos ni las acciones asociadas, lo que podr\u00eda dejar intactos los metadatos, las taxonom\u00edas y otros datos vinculados relacionados, lo que podr\u00eda generar elementos hu\u00e9rfanos adicionales."],"Performance settings":["Ajustes de rendimiento"],"Help":["Ayuda"],"Docs":["Documentos"],"Expand sidebar":["Abrir la barra lateral"],"Collapse sidebar":["Cerrar la barra lateral"],"Proceed":["Proceder"],"Processing ...":["Procesando ..."],"Check license status":["Comprobar el estado de la licencia"],"Successful":["Correcto"],"Close":["Cerrar"],"Keep Last":["Mantener el \u00faltimo"],"Import completed":["Importaci\u00f3n com